Given a 3 x 3 grid
Then cell at 1, 1 should be dead
And the cells around 1, 1 should have 0 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
When cell at 1, 1 is alive
Then cell at 1, 1 should be alive
And the cells around 1, 1 should have 0 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
When cell at 1, 2 is alive
Then cell at 1, 2 should be alive
And the cells around 1, 1 should have 1 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
When cell at 1, 1 is alive
And cell at 1, 2 is alive
Then cell at 1, 1 should be alive
And cell at 1, 2 should be alive
And the cells around 1, 1 should have 1 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
Then the cells around 0, 0 should have 0 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
Then the cells around 2, 2 should have 0 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
Then the cells around 0, 2 should have 0 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
Then the cells around 2, 0 should have 0 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
When cell at 1, 1 is alive
Then the cells around 2, 2 should have 1 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
When cell at 1, 1 is alive
And cell at 1, 2 is alive
Then the cells around 2, 2 should have 2 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
When cell at 2, 2 is alive
Then the cells around 0, 0 should have 0 live neighbors

Given a 3 x 3 grid
When cell at 0, 0 is alive
When cell at 0, 1 is alive
When cell at 0, 2 is alive
When cell at 1, 0 is alive
When cell at 1, 1 is alive
When cell at 1, 2 is alive
When cell at 2, 0 is alive
When cell at 2, 1 is alive
When cell at 2, 2 is alive
Then the cells around 1, 1 should have 8 live neighbors
